OL,3,CJob losses at Wedgwood described as
OL,4,C'blow' for sector
OL,6,FJobs are to be cut at ceramics firm
OL,7,FWedgwood in what GMB Union has
OL,8,Fdescribed as a "body blow" for the
OL,9,Fsector.
OL,11,FThe exact number of job losses is yet
OL,12,Fto be confirmed.
OL,14,FWedgwood had begun a 90-day pause in
OL,15,Fproduction in September, with 70
OL,16,Femployees placed on temporary leave.
OL,18,FAt the time Fiskars Group, which runs
OL,19,FWedgwood ceramics, said: "Our
OL,20,Femployees are extremely important.
