OL,3,CJob losses at Wedgwood described as
OL,4,C'blow' for sector
OL,6,F"You don't know what is happening in
OL,7,Fthe world economy. I can't say for
OL,8,Fsure the economy will change, but
OL,9,FWedgwood has a commitment to be made
OL,10,Fin England."
OL,12,FThe factory produces high-end and
OL,13,Fbespoke products, including
OL,14,Fhandcrafted pieces in fine bone china
OL,15,Fand its signature Jasperware.
OL,17,FWorkers still use techniques pioneered
OL,18,Fby founding English pottery designer
OL,19,Fand manufacturer Josiah Wedgwood, who
OL,20,Fwas born in Burslem, Staffordshire, in
OL,21,F1730.
