OL,3,CJob losses at Wedgwood described as
OL,4,C'blow' for sector
OL,6,FThe pottery and ceramics sector has
OL,7,Fbeen hit hard by rising costs and
OL,8,Fenergy bills in recent years, with a
OL,9,Fnumber of firms collapsing, including
OL,10,Fnearly-200 year old company Royal
OL,11,FStafford in February.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Chris Hoofe, GMB
OL,14,FOrganiser, said: "This is another body
OL,15,Fblow for ceramics in Staffordshire and
OL,16,Fmore evidence, if any was needed, to
OL,17,Fmeet GMB's demands of the government
OL,18,Fto act and support the sector.
