OL,3,CJob losses at Wedgwood described as
OL,4,C'blow' for sector
OL,6,F"GMB will be entering into
OL,7,Fconsultation over the proposed
OL,8,Fredundancies and fighting to mitigate
OL,9,Fany compulsory job losses.
OL,11,F"The workers at Wedgewood are highly
OL,12,Fskilled and dedicated employees who
OL,13,Fare affected by circumstances beyond
OL,14,Ftheir control.
OL,16,F"GMB Union will do everything we can
OL,17,Fto support them at this incredibly
OL,18,Fdifficult time."
OL,20,FITV Central has approached Wedgwood
OL,21,Ffor fresh comment.
